summary:
A simple replacement of default male to female mannequin from Vanilla + HearthFires. Seems to work with other DLC, pls refer long desription.
Changed Race to Nord. (see Pictures)
descriptionHtml:
Update
A simple replacement of default male to female mannequin from Vanilla + HearthFires.
Seems to work with Dragonborn.  Please confirm,(or nonconfirm)  also with Dawnguard ...

Changed Race to Nord. (see Pictures)

Should work with all Bodymods. (I did not know, why it should not ;) )
